Right Click windows icon
Choose Terminal(Admin) to open Windows powershell windows, Click Yes
// install git on PC
winget install --id Git.Git -e --source winget
git --version
// gives a valid response if git is correctly installed
// git version 2.51.0.windows.1

// install python on PC
winget install Python.Python.3.11
python --version
// python 3.11.9

// install ivarcus Verilog Simulation environment
using a browser go to https://bleyer.org/icarus/
click on the latest windows version eg iverilog-v12-20220611-x64_setup.exe
// https://bleyer.org/icarus/iverilog-v12-20220611-x64_setup.exe
Download on your PC
Click downloaded executable to install
// verify installation
iverilog -v
// Icarus Verilog version 12.0 (stable)

// install gtkwave
Using a browswer go to https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtkwave/files/
Look for a version with win64 in it e.g gtkwave-3.3.100-bin-win64
// https://sourceforge.net/projects/gtkwave/files/gtkwave-3.3.100-bin-win64/
Click downloaded executable to install
// verify installation
gtkwave --version
// GTKWave Analyzer v3.3.100 (w)1999-2019 BSI
